    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major restoration project or a reliable source of parts. The exterior has extensive rust damage, particularly around the wheel wells and undercarriage, and the paint is severely faded with multiple deep scratches and dents. Mechanically, the engine requires significant work to be roadworthy, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and some electronic components are non-functional. It is being sold strictly as-is.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you may find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small door ding consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it remains very solid, with a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has received all its scheduled oil changes. This is a reliable, well-cared-for car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a showroom-quality vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This specimen is in pristine condition, boasting a flawless exterior and an interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every surface has been preserved with exacting care, and the mechanical performance is as sharp and responsive as the day it left the factory. For the discerning buyer seeking a turn-key experience and a vehicle that represents the absolute pinnacle of its class, this is an unrivaled opportunity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she\u2019ll be just as pampered as she was with me. I\u2019ve kept this gem tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, and honestly, she looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint has that deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is absolutely pristine\u2014it\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, maintained with an open checkbook. There might be a tiny, almost invisible speck from the road if you look with a magnifying glass, but that\u2019s just a sign of a car that's ready to be enjoyed! Come by, let\u2019s grab a coffee, and I\u2019ll show you why this is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-tier E92 M3, a final-run specimen of the high-revving S65 atmospheric V8. This chassis is surgically clean, exhibiting zero subframe fatigue and a pristine undercarriage. The engine has been proactively serviced with VAC-treated rod bearings and ARP hardware to eliminate the platform's primary failure point. Throttle actuators have been upgraded to gear-driven units for permanent reliability. The M-Double Clutch Transmission (DCT) has been recalibrated with GTS-spec software for crisp, rev-matched downshifts and zero-lag engagement. Suspension kinematics are tight, featuring refreshed bushings and a laser-aligned geometry that delivers exceptional turn-in bite. Fluid analysis reports confirm optimal thermal stability and minimal metallic particulate. This is a turn-key, mechanically optimized machine for the driver who demands peak volumetric efficiency and uncompromising structural rigidity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom quality. Zero issues. First to see will buy. No lowballers.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it's a portal to a golden era of motoring. Imagine the low thrum of the engine echoing off coastal cliffs as the sun dips below the horizon, glinting off the deep, mirror-like finish of its curves. Inside, the rich aroma of hand-stitched leather and the tactile click of chrome toggles transport you to a time when driving was an art form. Every inch of this masterpiece exudes a quiet, commanding elegance, preserved like a secret kept just for you. It doesn't just travel; it arrives, leaving a trail of whispered admiration in its wake.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive excellence with this impeccably preserved specimen. Maintained to a rigorous showroom standard, this vehicle boasts a flawless exterior and an interior that retains its original factory freshness. Every detail, from the precision-engineered powertrain to the premium cabin finishes, reflects a history of uncompromising care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning driver to acquire a vehicle in pristine, investment-grade condition.",
      "price": 46850.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
